1
00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:04,880
Do you know what it means to dis Sabertooth?

2
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:07,700
I'm going to teach you with her body!

3
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:10,160
Stop this!

4
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:12,030
She'll destroy 
the Celestial Spirit wizard!

5
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:14,360
Stop the competition!

6
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:18,250
The referee has stopped it!

7
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:20,250
The competition is over!

8
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:22,350
The winner is Minerva!

9
00:00:22,350 --> 00:00:25,390
Sabertooth really is strong!

10
00:00:25,850 --> 00:00:29,880
Lucy hasn't moved for a 
while, but is she okay?!

11
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,890
Lucy!

12
00:02:13,390 --> 00:02:14,300
Are you okay?!

13
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,690
Hang in there!

14
00:02:15,690 --> 00:02:18,280
How could you do this to her, you witch?!

15
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:21,030
Get the Celestial Spirit Wizard 
to the infirmary immediately!

16
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:24,160
No! I'll give her emergency treatment first!

17
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,290
I'll help you!

18
00:02:25,290 --> 00:02:27,290
Lucy, hang in there!

19
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,420
What are you staring at?

20
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:37,890
Lucy-san!

21
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:41,380
She's terribly wounded, but 
if we do it together...

22
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:48,230
I asked you, what are you looking at?

23
00:02:48,950 --> 00:02:52,900
I acted within the rules of the competition.

24
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:54,390
Rules, you say?

25
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:58,180
You mean torturing an 
opponent who's already lost?

26
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:02,450
The crowd ate it up, didn't they?

27
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:06,030
Lucy should be grateful.

28
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:08,120
I let her be in second place.

29
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:11,080
Even though the girl is a 
useless piece of garbage...

30
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,280
What?!

31
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,760
Uh-oh! What's this?!

32
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:31,690
Are both teams about to rumble?!

33
00:03:32,690 --> 00:03:34,470
They're gonna start somethin' here?!

34
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:37,650
Sabertooth versus Fairy Tail!

35
00:03:38,690 --> 00:03:41,200
We need to keep things calm here.

36
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,290
But the crowd loves it!

37
00:03:43,290 --> 00:03:45,160
Thank you very much!

38
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:49,220
This is one of those unavoidable 
fate things, y'know?

39
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:51,370
Fro thinks so, too...

40
00:03:51,370 --> 00:03:53,500
This isn't an official match.

41
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:55,760
If they really do this, 
we'll go out there, too.

42
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:56,930
Aye, sir!

43
00:03:56,930 --> 00:03:58,750
Calm down, for crying out loud!

44
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,820
Wild...

45
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,380
...Four!

46
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:07,850
Things are getting pretty 
lively around here-kabo...

47
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:09,300
What should we do?

48
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,430
Lucy...

49
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:12,200
Men...

50
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:37,420
Fight! Fight! Fight! Fight!

51
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:35,940
I don't care if you're the 
strongest or number one in Fiore,

52
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:37,420
I'll just tell you one thing.

53
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,300
You people...

54
00:04:43,210 --> 00:04:46,800
...have made an enemy out of the one 
guild you don't want to anger.

55
00:04:58,490 --> 00:05:00,840
The Perfume I Dedicate to You!

56
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,880
Lucy, are you alright?

57
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,100
Is Lucy okay?!

58
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,000
Lucy!

59
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,340
You guys...

60
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:22,480
Even though we're on different 
teams, we're all in the same guild.

61
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:26,260
Laxus!

62
00:05:27,710 --> 00:05:29,260
So, how is she?

63
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:32,920
Thanks to Wendy, her life isn't in danger.

64
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:36,390
No, it was because of Cheria's 
emergency treatment.

65
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,930
Thank goodness...

66
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:41,170
And it looks like her major wounds 
are gone, so I'm relieved.

67
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,280
Those bastards...

68
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:46,230
I know what you wanna say...

69
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:49,030
Lucy...

70
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,490
Everyone... I'm sorry.

71
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:03,840
Why are you apologizin'?

72
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,420
I blew it again...

73
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:10,090
What are you talking about?! We took 
second place thanks to you, Lucy!

74
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:12,010
We got eight points!

75
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:14,180
Yeah. You did very well.

76
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,640
My keys...

77
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,100
Here they are.

78
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:24,830
Thank goodness! Thank you!

79
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:31,300
Looks like she fell asleep...

80
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,740
It's like they've got us all feeling down...

81
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:36,450
Sabertooth...

82
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:38,330
I don't like 'em...

83
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:41,880
Master!

84
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:45,630
A team, B team... You're all here?

85
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:47,170
Good.

86
00:06:49,450 --> 00:06:52,430
I'm not sure if this is 
good news or bad news.

87
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:58,480
The administrators told me that 
teams A and B must combine.

88
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,370
What?!

89
00:06:59,370 --> 00:07:01,600
Teams A and B have to unite?

90
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,120
Why?

91
00:07:04,350 --> 00:07:08,360
The disqualification of Raven Tail brings 
the number of teams down to seven,

92
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:12,340
and having an odd number doesn't work when 
it comes to matching up for the battle part.

93
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:16,440
Therefore, both of our teams must become one

94
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:19,830
and we have to choose the five members again.

95
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:22,150
Choose five members?

96
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,880
What about our points?

97
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,250
Apparently, the lower score will carry over.

98
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:30,130
In other words, A team's 35 points...

99
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:31,630
How cruel!

100
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:35,350
But if that's the administration's decision, 
there's nothing we can do about it.

101
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:40,030
Well, looking at the bright side, we'll be 
able to put together an even stronger team.

102
00:07:40,290 --> 00:07:42,750
But even if we decide on five people here,

103
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:46,150
the remaining events will all 
just be tag-team battles, right?

104
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:50,140
No. I'm sure that between tomorrow's 
break and the final day,

105
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,630
there will be a battle 
involving all five members.

106
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:55,160
So you should choose carefully.

107
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:58,270
I'm definitely gonna get revenge for Lucy!

108
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:05,920
I ain't gonna let 'em get away 
with laughin' at one of our own!

109
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:12,860
The Fairy Tail team has 
finished its reorganization,

110
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:15,990
and we're about to begin the 
battle part of day four!

111
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:20,370
Continuing with commentary, we have with 
us former Council member Yajima-san.

112
00:08:20,370 --> 00:08:21,140
Thank you.

113
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:26,090
And our special guest today is Rabian-san, leader 
of the Scheherazade Theatrical Troupe.

114
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:29,070
The Grand Magic Games
X791

115
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:29,070
It's an honor. Thank you very much.

116
00:08:29,330 --> 00:08:32,740
The battle part for the fourth 
day are tag-team matches, right?

117
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:35,550
Two against two? I can't wait!

118
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:37,560
Thank you very much!

119
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:41,160
Alright, I will now announce 
the match-ups for the battles!

120
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:44,230
Everyone, please direct your 
eyes to Lacrima-Vision!

121
00:08:44,230 --> 00:08:49,790
The first match is Blue 
Pegasus versus Quatro Puppy!

122
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:55,910
The second match is Mermaid 
Heel versus Lamia Scale!

123
00:08:56,700 --> 00:09:01,870
The third match is Sabertooth 
versus Fairy Tail!

124
00:09:02,690 --> 00:09:07,460
And now, here comes the new Fairy Tail team!

125
00:09:09,810 --> 00:09:12,360
Good luck, everyone.

126
00:09:15,330 --> 00:09:16,570
I'm countin' on you guys.

127
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:22,370
This really is the strongest team, right?

128
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:26,270
I'll be cheering you on!

129
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,420
Do your best!

130
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:32,290
This is an awesome team!

131
00:09:32,290 --> 00:09:35,010
I can't even picture these members failing.

132
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:44,520
The thoughts of our guild have become one.

133
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:48,960
We're entrusting this feeling to the gods!

134
00:09:51,110 --> 00:09:53,260
Now is the time to show them all

135
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:56,030
the power of our bond!

136
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,990
The whole arena is shaking!

137
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,600
Right here and now...

138
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:12,000
...Fairy Tail is taking the field!

139
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,250
As you might expect,

140
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:49,480
everyone's waiting for Fairy Tail versus 
Sabertooth, who were nearly about to brawl.

141
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:52,020
I didn't know what was going to happen then.

142
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:54,980
It certainly was a heated 
moment. Thank you very much.

143
00:10:58,220 --> 00:11:00,680
The Celestial Spirit Wizard isn't there.

144
00:11:01,010 --> 00:11:03,100
Apparently, she's in the infirmary.

145
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:06,680
Don't you even think about any 
heavy-handed action like last time!

146
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:08,550
Oh, no.

147
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:11,190
Admittedly, that was a blunder.

148
00:11:11,190 --> 00:11:14,690
Next time, I shall use a 
somewhat more reliable means.

149
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:18,280
But for the moment, let's enjoy the festival.

150
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:21,280
The plan will be set in 
motion three days hence.

151
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,040
Eclipse...

152
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:25,390
It will change the world.

153
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:29,910
And already, there is no way to stop it?

154
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:33,630
Lord Zeref is waiting...

155
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,020
I'm fired up.

156
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:05,080
Festival, eh?

157
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:11,840
The Grand Magic Games...

158
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:15,420
Although it once went by another name...

159
00:12:24,130 --> 00:12:25,930
The Festival of the Dragon King...

160
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:30,830
A feast for dragons, humans, and demons...

161
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:44,950
Alright, the first tag-team battle!

162
00:12:48,430 --> 00:12:51,370
From Blue Pegasus, Ichiya and Rabbit

163
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:56,380
versus Bacchus and Rocker from Quatro Puppy!

164
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,510
Wild...

165
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,510
...Four!

166
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:12,760
Bacchus-san, let's get wild with these guys.

167
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,700
At the rate we're goin'...

168
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:19,700
What? My soul is quivering. That's enough.

169
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:26,620
Well?

170
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:33,450
O-Oh, my! This is beautiful...

171
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:36,630
Opponents shaking hands before 
what's sure to be a fierce battle!

172
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:39,990
Too beautiful for words! Thank you very much!

173
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:42,260
The rabbit and I are gonna...?

174
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:45,160
His hand smells kinda good-four...

175
00:13:45,770 --> 00:13:49,390
At last, the time has come to unleash you.

176
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,830
The rabbit!

177
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:54,220
We'll finally find out who it really is!

178
00:13:59,690 --> 00:14:02,770
<i>We</i> don't even know who the rabbit is...

179
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:04,400
Who could it be...

180
00:14:05,050 --> 00:14:06,780
What the hell are you two doing?!

181
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:09,660
Please pay attention to Ichiya-san's match!

182
00:14:10,410 --> 00:14:12,180
Go ahead and show them...

183
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:14,120
...that handsome face!

184
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:41,750
He's...

185
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,150
...Extalia's...

186
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:49,110
Double Handsome Attack!

187
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,220
No way!

188
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:53,300
Gross!

189
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,430
Nichiya?!

190
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,040
This is a dangerous...

191
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,080
...parfum!

192
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:09,530
There are...

193
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:13,480
Double Handsome Attack!

194
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,990
...two Ichiyas?!

195
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:16,970
Pull yourself together!

196
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:19,170
That's not wild at all!

197
00:15:19,170 --> 00:15:22,940
In the first place, you're disqualified if 
somebody outside of Blue Pegasus participates!

198
00:15:23,850 --> 00:15:25,130
Look!

199
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:29,660
Before the Grand Magic Games began,

200
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:33,050
Nichiya-chan became a full-fledged 
member of our guild!

201
00:15:33,050 --> 00:15:37,440
With looks like that, he's plenty 
qualified to be one of us!

202
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:41,160
But how did Nichiya end 
up joining Blue Pegasus?

203
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,030
It was an encounter with myself...

204
00:15:44,430 --> 00:15:46,660
It was fate indeed.

205
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:50,420
Yes. It happened one sunny afternoon...

206
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:56,240
Sensing the parfum of an attractive 
person, I entered a forest.

207
00:15:57,050 --> 00:16:00,840
I walked on and on, but nothing appeared...

208
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,940
It was then I thought that perhaps...

209
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:07,830
...I was lost parfum-men!

210
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:12,110
So I tried to leave,

211
00:16:12,350 --> 00:16:14,660
but only succeeded in walking 
deeper and deeper into the forest.

212
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:17,460
Finally, starving and 
dehydrated, I collapsed.

213
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,450
But luckily,

214
00:16:21,450 --> 00:16:26,590
that forest was the abode of 
Exceeds who came to Earthland.

215
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,130
What a beautiful human!

216
00:16:31,610 --> 00:16:33,470
What a beautiful cat!

217
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:37,160
Hey! Get a grip!

218
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:41,080
Is there something that you'd like?

219
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:43,100
A glass of water...

220
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:44,630
Sure. Right away.

221
00:16:46,410 --> 00:16:48,400
Refreshing at a time like this...

222
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:50,410
Little did I know that this development

223
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:53,390
would become a classic romantic drama parfum.

224
00:16:56,570 --> 00:16:57,750
I'm sorry.

225
00:16:58,810 --> 00:17:01,900
Thanks to that, I'm refreshed-men.

226
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:04,630
I'm glad to hear that-men.

227
00:17:04,990 --> 00:17:05,500
Men...

228
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,040
Men!

229
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:08,350
Men...

230
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:09,660
Men!

231
00:17:10,150 --> 00:17:11,140
Men...!

232
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:16,800
This is the parfum of passionate friendship.

233
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:21,950
Until you recover your strength, 
refresh yourself here in this forest.

234
00:17:24,490 --> 00:17:29,680
And so, our friendship deepened even more.

235
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:32,470
It's the parfum of memories 
that are just too beautiful.

236
00:17:40,750 --> 00:17:43,290
What did you do?!

237
00:17:43,290 --> 00:17:45,650
Men!

238
00:17:45,650 --> 00:17:47,920
Ichiya-san! Can he even fight?!

239
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:49,840
Naturally!

240
00:17:50,310 --> 00:17:52,340
He's got the same face as me!

241
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:56,800
In other words...

242
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:59,450
...he's got the same fighting strength!

243
00:18:07,570 --> 00:18:09,770
Looks to me like he's dead!

244
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:15,550
It can't be!

245
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:18,950
Four... Time to stop messin' around...

246
00:18:18,950 --> 00:18:21,510
For us, it's now or never,

247
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,630
so we're gonna win this.

248
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:27,160
Suddenly the revealed 
identity of the bunny is down!

249
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:29,010
That makes it two against one.

250
00:18:29,010 --> 00:18:31,030
Game over, then?

251
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:32,860
Thank you very much!

252
00:18:34,490 --> 00:18:36,580
Hold on, you two!

253
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:39,950
Drilling rock for you!

254
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:43,860
Drunken Cleaving Hook Palm, Under the Moon!

255
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,510
Men!

256
00:18:47,520 --> 00:18:48,630
Ichiya...

257
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:52,610
Nichi...ya...

258
00:18:52,610 --> 00:18:54,630
It's gonna be over now!

259
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,500
Eat this!

260
00:18:56,500 --> 00:19:00,340
I got you involved in this battle...

261
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:03,820
I didn't realize you were a 
gentleman who couldn't fight...

262
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:07,810
Drilling rock for you!

263
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,390
And yet,

264
00:19:10,730 --> 00:19:13,880
you chose the path of fighting alongside us.

265
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:18,340
And you're incredibly handsome...

266
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:21,300
Why are you on the ground?

267
00:19:21,990 --> 00:19:24,370
Why are you hurt?!

268
00:19:28,490 --> 00:19:31,230
Oh, boy! Is this the end of the match?!

269
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:37,300
First the cat in the bunny suit, 
now Blue Pegasus's Ichiya is down!

270
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:39,180
Wild...

271
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:41,320
...Four!

272
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,640
Wait, not yet!

273
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:47,200
It looks like Ichiya of Blue 
Pegasus is going to stand up!

274
00:19:48,610 --> 00:19:52,290
I won't let your feelings go to waste!

275
00:19:53,950 --> 00:19:56,100
Handsomeness is justice!

276
00:20:02,870 --> 00:20:04,850
Muscle-men!

277
00:20:04,850 --> 00:20:07,090
Men-men-muscle-men!

278
00:20:07,090 --> 00:20:09,720
Muscle-men-men!

279
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:17,760
H-How'd he suddenly turn wild...?

280
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:20,110
That's the power of parfum!

281
00:20:20,850 --> 00:20:22,470
I dedicate this to you...

282
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:25,900
The parfum called victory!

283
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,580
Ichiya-san?!

284
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:34,740
This is kind of touching...

285
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,360
...kabo...

286
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:38,670
Wild Four!

287
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:41,860
Drilling rock for you!

288
00:20:41,860 --> 00:20:44,480
My soul is quivering!

289
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:46,590
Drunken Cleaving Hook Palm!

290
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:49,750
Take this! It's my...

291
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:51,770
...Beautiful Dreamer!

292
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:57,500
Smile!

293
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:01,760
Smash!

294
00:21:11,150 --> 00:21:14,460
Down! Quatro Puppy is down!

295
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:17,480
The winner is Blue Pegasus!

296
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,360
Men!

297
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,880
Against Bacchus...

298
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:27,800
He won, two against one...

299
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:29,850
It looks like he's not just an idiot.

300
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:31,890
Nah, he's awesome!

301
00:21:31,890 --> 00:21:34,720
How handsome can you get?

302
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:36,650
That's our blue angel.

303
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:38,580
He's so cool!

304
00:21:38,870 --> 00:21:40,440
I knew Ichiya-san could do it!

305
00:21:41,650 --> 00:21:43,640
Are you okay, Nichiya?

306
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:46,730
Wasn't very... Men... of me...

307
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:49,880
Wow, what a great match, huh?

308
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:51,720
I-I suppose...?

309
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:55,600
It was extremely disgusting. 
Thank you very much.

310
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:57,960
Alright, on to the second match!

311
00:21:57,960 --> 00:22:01,230
Lyon and Yuka from Lamia Scale!

312
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:09,550
Versus Kagura and Millianna 
from Mermaid Heel!

313
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:16,480
Lyon and Kagura, huh? This 
should be interesting.

314
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:57,900
Alright, on to the second match.

315
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:00,700
Commentator Natsu-san, what do you 
have to say about this match-up?

316
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:03,400
Lyon often picks fights with 
Gray, so he's okay in my book!

317
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,960
Regarding Yuka, back when 
we were on Galuna Island,

318
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:07,150
he shot me with that shocking thing.

319
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:07,940
Uh-huh...

320
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:10,070
I don't know about Kagura!

321
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:12,470
Millianna's easy to beat, 'cause all 
you gotta do is dress like a cat

322
00:24:12,470 --> 00:24:13,470
and she goes gooey-eyed!

323
00:24:14,100 --> 00:24:16,770
Next time: Battle of the Dragon Slayers!

324
00:24:17,170 --> 00:24:21,060
Thank you, Natsu-san! I knew you would 
explain in a way that's easy to understand.

325
00:24:22,390 --> 00:24:24,910
It was nothin'!

326
00:24:24,910 --> 00:24:26,910


